{"tid":1004233,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★$4000 政府率先向區議員收集表格　是否早交表早攞錢？","createTime":"2019-02-01T09:40:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-01T10:16:52.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"12ecdb162a2b277bb0336351c704c83ff75f1a4a","tid":1004233,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T09:40:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2390269/org/8fa3ab52b60d59765b1f74daeeceee71.jpg/L5is9D-w4Rg4Er8ECyplhVuSulH9bUM4rVXCbq1Vwm4\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2390269%2Forg%2F8fa3ab52b60d59765b1f74daeeceee71.jpg%2FL5is9D-w4Rg4Er8ECyplhVuSulH9bUM4rVXCbq1Vwm4&h=68aa6d89&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n政府自本月21日起派發領取4000元的申請表，遭外界批評手續繁複，多區區議員辦事處需免費為街坊影印表格及教填表。黃大仙區議員、民協主席施德來接受查詢時指，現時接獲約1000份申請表格，今日會再幫街坊核對資料，若有問題即聯絡街坊更改。對於區議員辦事若收集200份或以上的表格，政府部門將會派人前來收集，他稱仍未接獲民政處通知，處方職員能否於明日前來接收表格。施德來稱，因不少街坊「心急」，若職員無法於明日前收集表格，將會直接到附近的工業貿易大樓或觀塘職津處總部遞交，笑言「一千份（表格）有成二、三百萬元（價值）喺身㗎」。<br />\n<br />\n對於政府日前<span style=\"color: red;\">新增公屋辦事處的投遞地點，他稱政府職員亦未能確實答覆，何時會到該些投遞箱接收申請表格</span>，「（隨時）無形中遲咗」。政府早前稱二月初交表，將會獲發短訊確認，他擔心政府若同時處理100萬份表格，未必能如預期中在4月初發放現金。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E6%94%BF%E6%83%85/290070/%E6%B4%BE%E9%8C%A24000%E8%9A%8A-%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E4%BB%8A%E7%8E%87%E5%85%88%E5%90%91%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E5%93%A1%E6%94%B6%E9%9B%86%E8%A1%A8%E6%A0%BC-%E6%98%AF%E5%90%A6%E6%97%A9%E4%BA%A4%E8%A1%A8%E6%97%A9%E6%94%9E%E9%8C%A2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E6%2594%25BF%25E6%2583%2585%2F290070%2F%25E6%25B4%25BE%25E9%258C%25A24000%25E8%259A%258A-%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E4%25BB%258A%25E7%258E%2587%25E5%2585%2588%25E5%2590%2591%25E5%258D%2580%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E5%2593%25A1%25E6%2594%25B6%25E9%259B%2586%25E8%25A1%25A8%25E6%25A0%25BC-%25E6%2598%25AF%25E5%2590%25A6%25E6%2597%25A9%25E4%25BA%25A4%25E8%25A1%25A8%25E6%2597%25A9%25E6%2594%259E%25E9%258C%25A2&d=onMv7Z%2BNYg7J2un5CxWxstmOP5%2FvN4RyP%2Fy1e26q30o%3D&h=ab378b9f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E6%94%BF%E6%83%85/290070/%E6%B4%BE%E9%8C%A24000%E8%9A%8A-%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E4%BB%8A%E7%8E%87%E5%85%88%E5%90%91%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E5%93%A1%E6%94%B6%E9%9B%86%E8%A1%A8%E6%A0%BC-%E6%98%AF%E5%90%A6%E6%97%A9%E4%BA%A4%E8%A1%A8%E6%97%A9%E6%94%9E%E9%8C%A2</a>"},{"pid":"11f5cc853d09cf160744e21b31ba42925d816a2b","tid":1004233,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T09:40:40.000Z","msg":"已交<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a769d0d40f766dd6547b0fa48b8a3f537aec5860","tid":1004233,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T09:50:01.000Z","msg":"First in -last out <br />\n<br />\n老貓中伏 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef054172236ad4c2d04e7fddaeead700d638a082","tid":1004233,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a769d0d40f766dd6547b0fa48b8a3f537aec5860","tid":1004233,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T09:50:01.000Z","msg":"First in -last out <br />\n<br />\n老貓中伏 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T10:16:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}